{"tid":705514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"單方面宣布獨立嘅地區, 成功例子有幾多?","createTime":"2018-06-17T08:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T08:37:53.000Z","uid":16970,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7453285349a0c71408f0cba6058a39b2006804","tid":705514,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"地區獨立有兩種, 一種係同主權國傾掂數嘅協議獨立, 世間上大部分獨立立國嘅國家都係咁; 第二種就係單方面宣布獨立, 即係晌冇得到主權國認同嘅情況下獨立.<br />\n<br />\n依種單方面宣布獨立, 成功嘅例子有幾多呢? 大家可以去依度睇睇:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unilateral_declaration_of_independence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FUnilateral_declaration_of_independence&d=RfqEjC4p9oIoQvPbz36vO%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b1b7e5c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unilateral_declaration_of_independence</a><br />\n<br />\n歸納結果, 單方面宣布獨立有四種結果:<br />\n<br />\n1. 成功成為獨立國家;<br />\n2. 被主權國重新控制;<br />\n3. 成為不被國際社會承認主權嘅主權爭議地區;<br />\n4. 成為鄰近國家政府嘅傀儡政權.<br />\n<br />\n由此可見, 單方面宣布獨立唔係一件易事."},{"pid":"00cf1a8790b7becb51c527930bd6571fabda23e3","tid":705514,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"香港島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.cc/kqn0zf3gh/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.cc%2Fkqn0zf3gh%2Fimage.jpg&h=cd3fddbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"887678c8a3f4c9e3b1a836c539671fc723f8aa63","tid":705514,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2d699dcf3c6ce692654a86ef1c6329e6b5f0f07","tid":705514,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"887678c8a3f4c9e3b1a836c539671fc723f8aa63","tid":705514,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"科索沃有聯合國維和部隊駐紮啊."},{"pid":"b8f5e5d76b9e97ed63d7463c50702d87884b